EVERYONE.name: [Name:][Help Command]
EVERYONE.description: [Description:][Command that helps use all other commands!]
examples: [Example: 1]($PREFIX$help) Shows all <$CURRENTBOT$'s> commands with permission level <EVERYONE> and <OP_ONLY> and <OWNER_ONLY>
[Example: 2]($PREFIX$help) <todo> Shows <$CURRENTBOT$'s> usage information for the todo command if it is in your permission level
